    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Book
    Represents a book in the library.
    BookDao
    Data Access Object (DAO) class for managing Book entities.
    BookTests
    Test suite for the Book entity and its relationship with Copy.
    Borrowing
    Represents a record that a user borrowed a particular copy of a book.
    BorrowingDao
    Data Access Object (DAO) class for managing Borrowing entities.
    BorrowingTests
    Test suite for Borrowing entity and its interactions with User, Book, and Copy.
    CopiesTests
    Test suite for Copy entity and its interactions with Book.
    Copy
    Represents a physical copy of a book in the library.
    CopyDao
    Data Access Object (DAO) class for managing Copy entities.
    Dao<T>
    Generic Data Access Object (DAO) interface that defines basic CRUD operations.
    DataBaseInsert
    Initializes and inserts data into the database to populate tables with sample data.
    Librarian
    Represents a librarian in the library system.
    LibrarianDao
    Data Access Object (DAO) class for managing Librarian entities.
    LibrarianGUI
    A GUI-based application for librarians to manage the library system.
    LibrarianTests
    Test suite for Librarian entity and its interaction with User.
    MainApp
    The main entry point for the library management system application.
    Publisher
    Represents a publisher entity in the library system.
    PublisherDao
    Data Access Object (DAO) class for managing Publisher entities.
    PublisherTests
    Test suite for Publisher entity and its interaction with Book.
    RoleChooser
    The RoleChooser class provides a graphical interface for users to select their role in the library system.
    User
    Represents an application user in the library system.
    UserDao
    Data Access Object (DAO) for managing User entities.
    UserGUI
    A GUI-based application for users.
    UserTests
    Test suite for the User entity, including CRUD operations and relationships with borrowings.
